# Each-Step Development Log

> **Purpose:** Track every atomic change made to this repo during active development sessions. This is the granular audit trail.

## Instructions

- Each entry records **one atomic change**: a single file edit, a command run, a test executed, a decision made.
- Format: `YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM MSK | <action> — <file-or-component> | <reason> | <outcome/follow-up>`
- Leave the raw log; do not squash entries into summaries here (summaries go in `significant-changes-summary.mdc`).
- If a step failed, note the error and the fix attempted.

## Log Convention

```
YYYY-MM-DD | <type> | <component> | <detail>
```

Types: `EDIT`, `RUN`, `TEST`, `INSTALL`, `FIX`, `REFACTOR`, `DOC`, `CONFIG`, `DECISION`, `REVERT`.

